name: 2nd International Conference on Aquaculture and Fisheries 2020
content: Herald Meetings with great pleasure organizing “2nd International Conference on Aquaculture and Fisheries 2019” scheduled on June 26-27, 2019 at Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia with the theme “Recent Trends in Aquaculture and Fisheries” Consequently, all are desirable, encouraged, participate and take part in “2nd International Conference on Aquaculture & Fisheries 2019" scheduled on June 26-27, 2019 at Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia and build a large success!!!
